Package: hadeda
Type: Package
Title: Hedera Hashgraph Tidyverse Client
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person(
    given = "Christiaan",
    family = "Pauw",
    email = "cjpauw@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Hadeda provides tidyverse-oriented wrappers around the Hedera
    Hashgraph Mirror Node REST API and gRPC services. It standardises
    argument names, response schemas, and authentication workflows so
    analysts can interact with Hedera using familiar R conventions.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
